Solve these problems with Java (Class, Object, Constructor, Method is 
mandatory, single level inheritance, multi-level inheritance)

a. WAP to reverse a number and sum of all numbers
b. WAP Java Program to right rotate the elements of an array
c. Java Program to print Odd and Even Numbers from an Array
d. WAP to count number of vowels in a string.
e. WAP to print smallest element from an array
f. WAP to print 3rd largest number from an array
